HAIKOU, June 22 (Xinhua) -- A tropical rain forest project isto start soon in south China's Hainan province.
Under the program tropical rain-forest trees will be planted,along with tropical fruit trees and economic trees.
KUNMING, June 23 (Xinhua) -- Xishuangbanna, one of China'slargest tropical rain forest reserves, will almost double its areato bring more wild plants and animals under protection.
KUNMING, April 8 (Xinhua) -- China's largest tropical rainforest, in the Xishuangbanna nature reserve in Yunnan Province,will get further protection when the reserve is enlarged from247,000 ha to 533,000 ha, according to Zhuang Yan, head of theXishuangbanna Dai Autonomous Prefecture.
